# ðŸš€ Full CI/CD Pipeline Project with AWS, GitHub Codespaces, Terraform & Jenkins

This project automates the deployment of a full-stack CI/CD pipeline using AWS infrastructure, GitHub Codespaces for development, Terraform for infrastructure-as-code, Jenkins for orchestration, and ECS/EKS for container deployment.

